  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Icon Callout Box: Light Blue #E6F0F9 box on White #ffffff (16px 25px padding), Brand Blue #00529b Nunito Sans 800 ~21px/28px left, vertically center; White 80px rounded badge with 48px Brand Blue stroke icon half-overlay left edge; copy avoids badge overlap; for proof points."
